Interface IWorkspaceConnection.IMarkAsMergedOp

All Superinterfaces:
IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOp
Enclosing interface:
IWorkspaceConnection
public static interface IWorkspaceConnection.IMarkAsMergedOp
extends IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOp

Configuration operation structure which indicates that by selecting an existing state (or the deleted state) effectively resolves a conflict in the workspace. Instances are manufactured by IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOpFactory, and used in IWorkspaceConnection#commit(IChangeSetHandle, Collection).
